%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%2213%20President%20Awards%2C%202%20Padma%20Shris%3A%20Meet%20the%20Mentor%20Behind%20200%20Brilliant%20Innovations%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EBrigadier%20(Retd)%20P%20Ganesham%20is%20a%20man%20on%20a%20mission.%20He%20travels%20to%20remote%20parts%20of%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20and%20Telangana%20to%20discover%20new%20innovations.%20The%20mentor%20conducts%20%E2%80%98Shodha%20Yatras%E2%80%99%20to%20identify%20rural%20talent%20through%20his%20organisation%20Palle%20Srujana%2C%20which%20he%20started%20in%20November%202005%20after%20retiring%20from%20the%20Indian%20Army.%20His%20aim%20was%20to%20identify%2C%20reach%20out%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F188547%2Fpadma-shri-grassroots-innovation-andhra-pradesh-telangana-mentor-rural-india%2F%5C%22%3Ehelp%20innovators%20%3C%2Fa%3Escale%20up%20their%20creations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20past%2018%20years%2C%20the%20retired%20Army%20man%20has%20identified%20and%20helped%20over%20200%20rural%20innovators%2C%20including%20Padma%20Shri%20awardee%20Chintakindi%20Mallesham.%20Mallesham%20created%20the%20Laxmi%20ASU%20machine%20to%20reduce%20the%20time%20and%20labour%20required%20to%20weave%20Pochampalli%20silk%20sarees.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20during%20his%20service%20in%20the%20Indian%20Army%20that%20the%20armoured%20fighting%20vehicle%20specialist%20first%20encountered%20the%20acumen%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F304574%2Fscientist-builds-ai-enabled-device-to-diagnose-diseases-pathology-sigtuple-medtech-startup%2F%5C%22%3Egrassroot%20innovators%20%3C%2Fa%3Ein%20soldiers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOut%20of%20the%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F325599%2Fmadurai-jiovio-healthcare-startup-pregnancy-risk-monitoring-device-rural-women-infant-mortality%2F%5C%22%3E%20200%20innovations%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20he%20has%20identified%20so%20far%2C%2026%20are%20ready%20for%20sale%2C%2024%20have%20patents%2C%2013%20have%20bagged%20President%20awards%2C%20and%202%20received%20Padma%20Shri%20awards.%20The%20prototypes%20of%20all%20these%20innovations%20are%20displayed%20in%20the%20Brigadier%E2%80%99s%20home%20in%20Vayupuri%2C%20Secunderabad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20helped%20the%20innovators%20shine%20in%20national%20exhibitions%20and%20competitions%2C%20and%20even%20get%20loans%20for%20manufacturing%20or%20scaling%20up.%20Till%20date%2C%20we%20have%20been%20able%20to%20generate%20almost%20four%20crore%20financial%20assistance%20for%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHere%E2%80%99s%20how%20Brigadier%20Ganesham%20has%20helped%20bring%20hundreds%20of%20remarkable%20innovations%20to%20light%3A%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed%20wp-block-embed-youtube%20wp-embed-aspect-16-9%20wp-has-aspect-ratio%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed__wrapper%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Ciframe%20data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll%20data-origheight%3D%5C%22270%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FgT6dxTYJVEo%3Fenablejsapi%3D1%26autoplay%3D0%26cc_load_policy%3D0%26cc_lang_pref%3D%26iv_load_policy%3D3%26loop%3D0%26modestbranding%3D0%26rel%3D0%26fs%3D1%26playsinline%3D0%26autohide%3D2%26theme%3Ddark%26color%3Dred%26controls%3D1%26%5C%22%20data-no-lazy%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20player%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%20data-origwidth%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22270%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692189942000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22http%3A%2F%2Fimg.youtube.com%2Fvi%2FgT6dxTYJVEo%2F0.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D327322%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Retired%20Brigadier%20P%20Ganesham%20travels%20across%20India%20to%20help%20identify%20over%20200%20grassroots%20innovators%20behind%20brilliant%20utilitarian%20device