0Bihar%2C%20Bindeshwar%20Pathak%20was%20exposed%20to%20the%20stark%20realities%20of%20social%20inequality%20from%20an%20early%20age.%20The%20pervasive%20practice%20of%20manual%20scavenging%20%E2%80%94%20where%20individuals%20from%20the%20so-called%20%E2%80%9Clower%20castes%E2%80%9D%20were%20forced%20to%20clean%20human%20waste%20%E2%80%94%20left%20an%20indelible%20mark%20on%20his%20young%20mind.%20This%20deeply%20ingrained%20injustice%20lit%20the%20spark%20that%20would%20ignite%20his%20life%E2%80%99s%20mission.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20960px)%20100vw%2C%20960px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F971079_518963701499082_1454533731_n-1692182167.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Bindeshwar%20Pathak%20provided%20employment%20opportunities%20to%20people%20from%20the%20marginalised%20communities.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F971079_518963701499082_1454533731_n-1692182167.jpg%20960w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F971079_518963701499082_1454533731_n-1692182167-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F971079_518963701499082_1454533731_n-1692182167-500x333.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F971079_518963701499082_1454533731_n-1692182167-768x512.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F971079_518963701499082_1454533731_n-1692182167-150x100.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-327299%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22640%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EBindeshwar%20Pathak%20provided%20employment%20opportunities%20to%20people%20from%20marginalised%20communities.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20journey%20of%20empathy%20and%20innovation%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPathak%E2%80%99s%20path%20to%20transformation%20was%20paved%20with%20empathy%20and%20innovation.%20Armed%20with%20a%20degree%20in%20sociology%2C%20he%20embarked%20on%20a%20mission%20to%20eradicate%20manual%20scavenging%20and%20uplift%20the%20marginalised.%20His%20groundbreaking%20idea%20of%20a%20two-pit%20pour-flush%20toilet%20not%20only%20eliminated%20the%20need%20for%20manual%20cleaning%20but%20also%20promoted%20safe%20waste%20disposal%20and%20biogas%20production.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%201970%2C%20he%20established%20the%20Sulabh%20Sanitation%20Movement%20%E2%80%94%20a%20revolutionary%20step%20towards%20creating%20clean%20and%20hygienic%20sanitation%20facilities%20accessible%20to%20all.%20Through%20his%20tireless%20efforts%2C%20thousands%20of%20toilets%20were%20constructed%20across%20India%2C%20transforming%20the%20lives%20of%20countless%20families.%20The%20movement%E2%80%99s%20impact%20extended%20beyond%20sanitation%2C%20fostering%20a%20sense%20of%20dignity%20and%20empowerment%20among%20the%20marginalised%20sections%20of%20society.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPathak%E2%80%99s%20work%20transcended%20bricks%20and%20mortar.%20By%20the%20year%202021%2C%20the%20Sulabh%20International%20Social%20Service%20Organisation%2C%20under%20his%20leadership%2C%20had%20successfully%20constructed%20and%20maintained%20over%201.5%20million%20household%20toilets%20in%20India.%20These%20facilities%20not%20only%20improved%20sanitation%20and%20hygiene%20but%20also%20created%20a%20massive%20ripple%20effect%20in%20terms%20of%20social%20and%20economic%20transformation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20most%20remarkable%20aspects%20of%20Pathak%E2%80%99s%20initiatives%20is%20the%20employment%20opportunities%20they%20have%20generated.%20The%20Sulabh%20movement%20has%20employed%20over%2050%2C000%20people%20from%20marginalised%20communities%2C%20including%20former%20manual%20scavengers.%20These%20individuals%20were%20given%20a%20chance%20to%20break%20free%20from%20th