On%20joining%20Adithi%20Millets%20the%20farmer%20adopted%20Somashekar%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2Fweb-stories%2F5-miracle-millets-that-helped-a-67-yo-control-her-diabetes%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ere-cropping%20method%3C%2Fa%3E%20(leaving%20six%20inches%20of%20stubble%20in%20the%20ground%20after%20harvest%20and%20allowing%20it%20to%20grow%20in%20the%20monsoon%20without%20sowing%20new%20seeds).%20This%20gave%20him%20yet%20another%20harvest%20of%204%2C000%20kg%20of%20brown%20top%20millets%2C%20which%20he%20then%20sold%20for%20Rs%207%2C000%20per%20quintal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20got%20almost%20double%20my%20previous%20revenue%20without%20sowing%20new%20seeds%2C%E2%80%9D%20exclaims%20the%20farmer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESomashekar%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20is%20glad%20he%20can%20help%20his%20community.%20His%20beliefs%20in%20good%20agricultural%20practices%20and%20a%20love%20for%20farming%20have%20stood%20the%20test%20of%20time%20and%20helped%20him%20scale%20his%20empire%20to%20what%20it%20is%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692021061000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Ffarming-1692018453.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D327220%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22When%20Somashekar%20Pogula's%20father%20passed%20away%20in%202013%2C%20it%20left%20a%20deep%20impact%20on%20him.%20In%20a%20bid%20to%20do%20something%20that%20would%20enable%20people%20to%20eat%20right%20and%20help%20farmers%20earn%20better%2C%20he%20started%20Adithi%20Millets%20in%20Kurnool%2C%20Andhra%20Pradesh.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Krystelle%20Dsouza%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F327220%2Fandhra-pradesh-somashekar-pogula-started-adithi-millets-empower-organic-farmers%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%2