nctuary%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fsai-2-1691587385.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20daily%20cost%20of%20feeding%20the%20animals%20and%20upkeep%20of%20the%20sanctuary%20is%20Rs%2018%2C000.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fsai-2-1691587385.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fsai-2-1691587385-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fsai-2-1691587385-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fsai-2-1691587385-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fsai-2-1691587385-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-326860%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20daily%20cost%20of%20feeding%20the%20animals%20and%20maintaining%20the%20sanctuary%20is%20Rs%2018%2C000%3B%20Picture%20credit%3A%20Sai%20Vignesh%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELooking%20for%20avenues%20and%20donations%2C%20Sai%20stumbled%20upon%20an%20ancestral%20home%20that%20belonged%20to%20his%20family.%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20determined%20to%20convince%20my%20parents%20to%20sell%20the%20house%20and%20help%20me%20with%20the%20funds.%20While%20it%20was%20a%20big%20decision%2C%20they%20could%20see%20that%20it%20was%20my%20only%20passion%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESai%20and%20his%20parents%20sold%20their%20ancestral%20home%20and%20purchased%20an%20eight-acre%20land%20near%20Poondi%20reservoir%20in%20Tiruvallur%20on%20the%20outskirts%20of%20Chennai.%20%E2%80%9CWith%20the%20help%20of%20some%20more%20donations%2C%20I%20was%20able%20to%20construct%20a%20safe%20haven%20for%20animals.%20The%20Almighty%20Animal%20Care%20Trust%20was%20inaugurated%20in%202019%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20his%20cause%20started%20with%20taking%20care%20of%20stray%20dogs%2C%20his%20care%20soon%20expanded%20to%20other%20animals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20realised%20that%20in%20Chennai%2C%20there%20were%20sanctuaries%20for%20dogs%2C%20but%20when%20it%20came%20to%20farm%20animals%2C%20they%20had%20nowhere%20to%20go.%20Many%20bulls%2C%20buffaloes%20and%20calves%20are%20abandoned%20by%20their%20owners.%20They%20roam%20in%20the%20city%2C%20consume%20polluted%20water%20and%20food%2C%20and%20end%20up%20in%20difficult%20conditions%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESai%20continues%2C%20%E2%80%9CIf%20a%20dog%20gets%20hit%20by%20a%20car%2C%20there%20is%20a%20chance%20it%20will%20get%20some%20kind%20of%20help.%20However%2C%20with%20animals%20like%20sheep%2C%20cows%20and%20buffaloes%2C%20they%20are%20most%20likely%20to%20end%20up%20in%20slaughterhouses.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20led%20Sai%20to%20open%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F316625%2Fruvuotuo-belho-builds-mini-zoo-in-kohima-nagaland-saves-birds-and-animals-from-hunting%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eup%20the%20sanctuary%20to%20any%20animal%20%3C%2Fa%3Ethat%20needs%20help.%20Presently%2C%20he%20has%20around%20250%20animals%20under%20his%20care%20%E2%80%94%20which%20include%20around%2080%20dogs%2C%2025%20goats%2C%20116%20cows%2C%20buffaloes%20and%20bulls%2C%204%20pigs%2C%20and%202%20horses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ERescuing%20and%20fighting%20for%20animal%20rights%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPeople%20reach%20out%20to%20Sai%20via%20his%20Facebook%20and%20Instagram%20pages%20to%20inform%20him%20about%20any%20animal%20in%20danger.%20Some%20volunteers%20usually%20accompany%20him%20to%20rescue%20the%20animals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COnce